Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.33,0:00:02.52,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,They're finished!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.87,0:00:04.50,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Let me see.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.50,0:00:05.87,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,They're finally here?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.87,0:00:06.74,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.74,0:00:07.86,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,They're so cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.87,0:00:10.30,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.71,0:00:15.94,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,My name is missing...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.38,0:00:19.71,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Why is mine the only one missing?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.38,0:00:23.84,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Our graduation shirts are supposed to stay with us for the rest of our lives...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.32,0:00:30.45,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Did they all hate me?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.83,0:00:32.83,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}They're so cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.23,0:00:32.83,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Or something...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.83,0:00:33.83,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}The material's pretty nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.83,0:00:35.63,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}The color's not bad, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.90,0:00:41.03,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Banri?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.70,0:00:42.67,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.84,0:00:45.83,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,My name...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.34,0:00:47.57,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.88,0:00:49.90,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,My name is missing!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.21,0:00:54.45,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It's true!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.45,0:00:55.71,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Banri's name is missing!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.68,0:00:57.45,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What? Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.45,0:00:58.22,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,That's awful.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.22,0:01:01.55,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,They'll replace them for free, won't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.42,0:01:05.79,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, we'll get them replaced.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.79,0:01:06.82,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Cheer up.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.03,0:01:10.43,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,F-for a second, I was afraid it was intentional...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.43,0:01:11.80,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.80,0:01:13.93,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Just how stupid are you, Banri?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.64,0:01:19.07,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really worried about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.08,0:01:24.01,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,After we graduate, we won't be together anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.98,0:01:26.28,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Will you be okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.28,0:01:28.11,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Can you make it on your own?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.13,0:01:40.53,Dialogue4,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\pos(360,89)}{\c&HFFFFFF&}Karaoke
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.80,0:01:48.36,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Whew!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.80,0:01:50.53,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,That was exciting.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.94,0:01:52.64,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone cried way too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.01,0:01:54.60,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It made me cry, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.74,0:01:59.54,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Banri, good luck on your entrance exams next year.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.75,0:02:02.85,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to Tokyo,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.85,0:02:05.08,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,but I'll help you study when I come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.29,0:02:08.28,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Yes or no.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.36,0:02:10.45,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.76,0:02:13.39,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.26,0:02:15.89,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,This will be the first and last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.26,0:02:18.82,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I want a simple answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.27,0:02:22.76,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to be apart from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.14,0:02:24.77,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I want to be with you all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.67,0:02:26.64,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.71,0:02:30.77,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,If you feel the same way,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.18,0:02:33.01,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go to a prep school in Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.15,0:02:35.74,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Yes or no.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.02,0:02:37.78,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me your answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.02,0:02:41.92,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Could you wait a little bit?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.12,0:02:45.32,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Can I think about it overnight?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.73,0:02:48.92,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.36,0:02:53.83,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'll wait for you on the usual bridge tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.74,0:03:00.30,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,In high school, I was in love with Linda.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.68,0:03:02.94,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I was serious about her,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.08,0:03:07.78,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,but the people around us saw us as siblings or friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.82,0:03:12.31,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Linda only thought of me as a friend, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.92,0:03:15.82,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,The same way that Kaga Kouko...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.82,0:03:20.69,Dialogue2,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an4\pos(317,306)}{\c&HFFFFFF&}Yes No
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.69,0:03:19.83,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,...calls Tada Banri her friend now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.00,0:03:24.20,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Hand in hand let's go party night!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.20,0:03:27.14,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Kokoro odoru tomerarenai no
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.57,0:03:33.91,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Naite waratte kimi to no kioku zutto wasurenai
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.28,0:03:43.88,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Hontou no jibun wa doko ni iru toka
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.75,0:03:47.24,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Otona ni narutte taihen de
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.96,0:03:50.86,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Ima wa wasurete mo ii kana
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.86,0:03:53.59,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Yoru ga matte iru kara
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.90,0:03:57.86,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Kokoro wo hazumase aeru toki wo
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.27,0:04:00.83,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Hashagi mawareba
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.20,0:04:04.37,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Tsutaetai omoi ni ima
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.97,0:04:08.00,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Kizuite shimaisou de
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.31,0:04:11.51,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Kako to mirai osorete ite mo
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.71,0:04:15.17,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Karappo no mama ja ugeokenai
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.48,0:04:21.86,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Tanoshimeba it's all right hajimeyou
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.32,0:04:28.35,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Yana koto zenbu wasurete kimi to issho ni odori akaseba
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.80,0:04:35.46,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Motto suteki na jibun ni nareru sonna ki ga suru no
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.07,0:04:41.98,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Owaranai Golden Time gyutto chikazuku kimi to no kyori wa
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.44,0:04:49.25,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Tsukazu hanarezu mawari michi demo taisetsu ni shitai
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.69,0:04:55.71,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,They fit perfectly!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.59,0:04:58.89,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,My feet feel so light.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.86,0:05:01.63,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,They fit someone?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.63,0:05:03.72,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,They didn't fit any of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.97,0:05:05.87,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Could he be Cinderella?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.10,0:05:07.44,Dialogue3,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an4\pos(53,46)}{\c&HFFFFFF&}Note: the white-eyed expression of shock are iconic of
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.10,0:05:07.44,Dialogue3,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\pos(336,75)}{\c&HFFFFFF&}the stage-drama, anime, and manga story, Glass Mask.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.03,0:05:08.84,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Are his feet the ones that fit the glass sneakers?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.84,0:05:13.07,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,This kid with the aura of a seedy and unpopular comedian saturating his genes?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.78,0:05:14.90,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Terrifying!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.11,0:05:16.91,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,So, where did these come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.21,0:05:20.28,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Someone wants to sell those sneakers.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.28,0:05:22.65,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,She said she'd sell them for five thousand yen if they fit.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.18,0:05:24.41,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Brand new and unused.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.89,0:05:27.45,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,They'd probably normally cost over twenty thousand.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.62,0:05:28.49,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Twenty thousand...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.62,0:05:30.96,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'll buy them!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.19,0:05:33.75,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, Tada-kun! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.46,0:05:35.12,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Kaga-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.50,0:05:37.62,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,...and Linda-senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.97,0:05:41.50,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Linda, Tada Banri said he'd buy these sneakers.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.50,0:05:42.63,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.24,0:05:45.67,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Linda-senpai, are these yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.67,0:05:46.64,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.14,0:05:48.17,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,How do they fit?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.38,0:05:50.11,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Perfectly.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.55,0:05:52.48,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Really? Okay, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.48,0:05:54.72,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,For Tada Banri, they're free.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.72,0:05:56.31,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You're "tada" Banri, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.72,0:05:56.31,Dialogue2,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an4\pos(276,380)}{\c&HFFFFFF&}("free")
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.82,0:05:57.82,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.82,0:05:58.59,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,That's not fair.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.59,0:06:00.32,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Well, he's our junior.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.32,0:06:02.49,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,A sweet, precious first year.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.49,0:06:04.48,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I can't take his money.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.26,0:06:05.99,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.43,0:06:10.99,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,They weren't my size, but it was love at first sight. It was an impulse buy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.87,0:06:14.13,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You should wear them instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.90,0:06:15.80,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.54,0:06:18.57,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.57,0:06:19.97,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.54,0:06:23.67,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.91,0:06:25.47,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Are you guys Awa dancing?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.08,0:06:27.85,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.75,0:06:27.85,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}Long time, no see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.85,0:06:29.35,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,They're fourth years.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.35,0:06:30.91,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,The former club leaders.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.35,0:06:32.75,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,How's the search for work going?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.75,0:06:34.36,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Have you already found jobs?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.36,0:06:36.22,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,We're just getting started, you idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.22,0:06:38.19,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,None of us have any offers yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.19,0:06:39.23,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It's not easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.23,0:06:40.53,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You'd better prepare yourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.90,0:06:44.59,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, did you bring us any goodies?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.77,0:06:45.86,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.57,0:06:48.16,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,We brought something.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.41,0:06:57.78,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You need these for the Awa dance, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.78,0:06:59.27,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.78,0:07:02.27,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,The fourth year students pooled their money to make these.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.78,0:07:04.62,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,He designed them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.62,0:07:06.95,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, smile!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.95,0:07:07.72,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you like them?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.22,0:07:09.69,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.96,0:07:13.52,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I hate you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.83,0:07:18.70,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Tada-kun, did something happen with Linda-senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.83,0:07:19.83,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.83,0:07:23.67,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Things just seemed a little weird earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.67,0:07:25.14,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Why would Linda-senpai and I...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.97,0:07:27.96,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You're imagining things.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.68,0:07:29.70,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.85,0:07:33.61,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,If you're worried about something, you can tell me about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.25,0:07:36.62,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,After all, we're friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.62,0:07:37.61,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.79,0:07:40.08,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Friends...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.69,0:07:42.49,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Banri, Kaga-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.02,0:07:44.62,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I finally found you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.03,0:07:46.89,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Okachi Nami...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.76,0:07:49.46,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You split it up wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.46,0:07:50.80,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It's not Okachi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.80,0:07:52.60,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It's Oka Chinami.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.00,0:07:56.04,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you come to our welcoming party today?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.04,0:07:58.34,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to have a blast with all of our friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.54,0:08:00.80,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the one who suggested it, so I'm organizing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.04,0:08:01.98,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah? Where-
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.98,0:08:03.61,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not going!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.61,0:08:04.58,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way I'd go!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.98,0:08:06.00,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.31,0:08:09.65,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Tada-kun, I'm going to class.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.29,0:08:15.19,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I knew she'd turn me down.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.19,0:08:17.66,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you want Kaga-san to go so badly?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.19,0:08:21.33,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Most people wouldn't, considering what happened the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.33,0:08:22.46,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.86,0:08:26.63,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Unless you're actually a really malicious person.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.54,0:08:29.77,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe you invited Kaga-san because you hate her,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.07,0:08:37.50,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,and you're planning to swallow her and chew her up like a Rafflesia enshrined deep in the jungle.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.85,0:08:39.38,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What? Why would I do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.38,0:08:40.87,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of creature am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.35,0:08:42.88,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I just...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.88,0:08:46.75,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,There's something I find irresistible about Kaga-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.75,0:08:49.52,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,And she's really pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.76,0:08:52.32,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,She's definitely really pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.59,0:08:55.50,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Yana's missing out.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.90,0:09:00.94,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Not being acknowledged by the person you love must be hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.94,0:09:04.74,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Since they attend the same college, they can't avoid each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.61,0:09:08.97,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure Kaga-san won't come?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.08,0:09:12.38,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'll try inviting her.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.51,0:09:16.41,Dialogue6,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an4\pos(393,135)}{\c&HFFFFFF&}Bar
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.51,0:09:16.41,Dialogue7,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an4\pos(339,205)}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\i1}GOLDENTIME{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.78,0:09:16.41,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so happy you're all here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.78,0:09:19.31,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,This'll be a great party!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.75,0:09:23.26,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'm your organizer and host, Oka Chinami!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.26,0:09:24.35,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Cheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.53,0:09:25.99,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,CHEERS!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.29,0:09:27.73,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.90,0:09:30.19,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,So these are all Oka-chan's friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.73,0:09:33.57,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It's not just first years here.\NThere are some older students, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.07,0:09:35.56,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Just how many people does she know?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.20,0:09:39.57,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,So, what are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.94,0:09:42.71,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,My friend Tada-kun convinced me to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.71,0:09:45.87,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,He said we should dive into all kinds of new things.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.91,0:09:50.04,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't your friends from the film club here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.42,0:09:51.68,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you go hang out with them?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.82,0:09:53.88,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Don't order me around.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.12,0:09:59.62,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,L-look, why don't you try to get along just for today?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.66,0:10:02.16,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.16,0:10:03.76,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It's complicated...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.63,0:10:07.43,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.40,0:10:12.07,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It's Hell in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.07,0:10:14.60,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,We didn't see anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.81,0:10:18.61,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you learn from Chinami?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.58,0:10:21.38,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.82,0:10:26.28,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'm saying you should change seats and try talking to different people.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.65,0:10:29.92,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You still don't have any other friends, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.19,0:10:32.69,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I do!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.69,0:10:35.70,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,The seniors in the festival club are nice to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.70,0:10:37.67,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Linda-senpai is really nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.17,0:10:41.27,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need to copy Miss Ultrasonic.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.27,0:10:42.94,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Don't call her that!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.94,0:10:46.81,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You'd never be able to gather this many people!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.81,0:10:48.83,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Well, neither could you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.48,0:10:50.71,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Besides,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.71,0:10:54.15,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,you're only pretending to like\NMiss Ultrasonic to spite me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.48,0:10:55.82,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.82,0:10:56.95,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}It's definitely true!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.98,0:10:58.15,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what happened,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.95,0:11:00.62,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}You just think it will hurt me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.15,0:11:01.28,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,but shouldn't we separate them?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.62,0:11:01.28,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}It has nothing to do with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.46,0:11:02.12,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.92,0:11:05.36,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}Just how overconfident are you, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.69,0:11:04.96,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,H-hey, Kaga-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.36,0:11:08.83,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}You'll never be able to confess your feelings to her!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.36,0:11:05.69,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Can you-
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.83,0:11:11.32,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}You don't have the resolve!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.70,0:11:13.50,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Don't assume I can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.67,0:11:15.80,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,If I'm wrong, why don't you prove it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.00,0:11:17.77,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I will!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.47,0:11:19.34,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Chinami!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.71,0:11:22.48,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Yana!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.48,0:11:24.91,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,And Kaga-san, thank you for coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.91,0:11:27.48,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.48,0:11:28.21,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Chinami.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.65,0:11:29.64,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.82,0:11:32.65,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.65,0:11:34.78,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I want to go out with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.16,0:11:37.28,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.76,0:11:41.79,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.53,0:11:43.62,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I want to go out with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.67,0:11:47.73,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.27,0:11:49.13,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.04,0:11:56.31,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,He's done it now...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.78,0:11:57.68,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.68,0:11:59.08,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Don't ask me...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.55,0:12:01.91,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,K-Kaga-san?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.35,0:12:04.68,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,H-he really did it...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.42,0:12:10.59,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Ladies, I have tribute for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.86,0:12:12.88,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Tada Banri, you're here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.03,0:12:15.19,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Tribute? What tribute?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.53,0:12:16.76,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,He's so hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.76,0:12:18.53,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.23,0:12:20.72,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Take her, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.24,0:12:23.33,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! It's that girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.64,0:12:26.87,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Her skin is so smooth and beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.87,0:12:27.78,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It looks delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.78,0:12:31.11,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,She's so cute, I just want to torment her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.71,0:12:35.08,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You're a monster, Banri.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.55,0:12:37.07,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.82,0:12:40.75,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,He sprung it on you...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.89,0:12:42.69,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.66,0:12:45.89,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Ta-da!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.89,0:12:47.63,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It's the Oka Chinami Camera!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.63,0:12:49.29,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,The Okamera for short!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.83,0:12:53.23,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I've been filming everyone with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.80,0:12:58.36,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to put it all together in a single film eventually.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.77,0:13:01.81,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right. You're in the film club.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.81,0:13:05.75,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,This is the only time we'll be new students at a university.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.31,0:13:08.15,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,These moments are precious.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.15,0:13:11.48,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, say something funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.09,0:13:14.02,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Uh... um...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.02,0:13:17.16,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'm 2D-kun, Sato Takaya.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.16,0:13:18.92,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'm nearsighted.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.16,0:13:20.59,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Next, Banri.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.93,0:13:22.59,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm Tada Banri.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.80,0:13:23.96,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'm alive, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.63,0:13:26.76,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I can't think of anything funny!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.67,0:13:29.60,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,That was fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.60,0:13:32.34,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Can I have your email address?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.10,0:13:32.34,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}The tea club's going out for a second round.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.34,0:13:33.77,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,This way if you're coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.77,0:13:35.40,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think I can...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.78,0:13:39.91,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,They met the same fate we did...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.55,0:13:45.35,Dialogue4,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an4\pos(441,209)}{\c&HFFFFFF&}Pedestrians
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.55,0:13:45.35,Dialogue2,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an4\pos(490,246)}{\c&HFFFFFF&}and
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.55,0:13:45.35,Dialogue4,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an4\pos(462,285)}{\c&HFFFFFF&}Bicycles
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.55,0:13:45.35,Dialogue2,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an4\pos(484,323)}{\c&HFFFFFF&}Only
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.05,0:13:47.75,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, Kaga-san. Walk.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.49,0:13:51.12,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I've got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.79,0:13:54.76,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, catch me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.73,0:13:57.70,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously, that's enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.24,0:14:04.60,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I don't feel so good.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.07,0:14:07.64,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to be sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.64,0:14:09.30,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Do it in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.72,0:14:15.98,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.18,0:14:18.71,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Kaga-san, please. Take a taxi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.85,0:14:21.32,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I want to have more fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.32,0:14:23.36,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You're my friend. Come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.36,0:14:26.06,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It's late, and I don't have any money.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.06,0:14:28.83,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Then let's go to your place.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.16,0:14:31.60,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Let's talk all night.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.60,0:14:34.07,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,About friendship and youth.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.74,0:14:36.70,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Let's badmouth Mitsuo, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.54,0:14:41.91,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Can we stop?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.24,0:14:43.01,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.68,0:14:45.74,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to be friends anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.21,0:14:48.01,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.92,0:14:51.02,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Say "yes".
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.02,0:14:53.89,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to be friends with you anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.29,0:14:58.36,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Yana-san is still all you think about.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.36,0:15:02.56,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Have you thought about how it makes me feel to see that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.10,0:15:07.90,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It's too hard for me to be with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.97,0:15:12.67,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not your friend anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.78,0:15:15.77,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.42,0:15:24.04,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Do you still want to be friends with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.62,0:15:28.82,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Is it because you feel comfortable being with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.82,0:15:32.56,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Because I understand your awkward and useless self,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.56,0:15:34.08,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,and still love you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.56,0:15:37.40,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Quit acting so spoiled.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.40,0:15:42.46,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,When you rejected me, you lost the right to want those things!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.67,0:15:46.20,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I shouldn't have tried to be your friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.14,0:15:49.27,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I can't associate with you anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.15,0:15:52.74,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.62,0:16:01.69,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.69,0:16:02.68,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I won't wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.29,0:16:04.66,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I won't wait for anyone anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.86,0:16:06.59,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Tada-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.70,0:16:08.75,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.30,0:16:10.73,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,She's riding.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.27,0:16:13.10,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Tada-kun, don't do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.10,0:16:15.37,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Please, listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.37,0:16:15.93,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.61,0:16:20.77,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.54,0:16:25.15,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Clean up!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.15,0:16:27.38,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,The next group is coming in to use this room.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.38,0:16:29.22,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Let's clean this place up and get out!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.22,0:16:30.81,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.32,0:16:36.56,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Tada Banri?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.56,0:16:38.62,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You seemed down today.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.89,0:16:39.76,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.36,0:16:43.56,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.03,0:16:45.53,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Did you have a fight with Kouko-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.56,0:16:44.70,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.33,0:16:48.13,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Linda, we're leaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.54,0:16:49.53,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.57,0:16:53.77,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Kouko-chan was looking at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.38,0:16:57.83,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't make your girlfriend so sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.71,0:17:02.65,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Linda-senpai... do you think we're dating?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.65,0:17:05.99,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you're so close.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.99,0:17:06.72,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,We're not.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.06,0:17:09.46,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.86,0:17:15.69,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,How can she act like she doesn't know anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.56,0:17:17.70,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.70,0:17:20.53,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You're more than friends, but not yet dating?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.60,0:17:25.04,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What about you, Linda-senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.74,0:17:28.38,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What... about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.38,0:17:30.28,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you have a boyfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.28,0:17:32.71,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe someone you've been dating since high school?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.95,0:17:34.88,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I ask...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.52,0:17:37.21,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure you'll tell me you don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.59,0:17:41.06,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,No one. You'll say there's no one!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.06,0:17:41.99,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You've erased him!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.52,0:17:45.73,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,How can you do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.73,0:17:47.76,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think it's cruel?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.76,0:17:52.53,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you feel bad for me... for the old Tada Banri?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.37,0:17:58.00,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'm doing the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.07,0:18:01.60,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I act like I don't know them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.04,0:18:07.00,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Not Linda-senpai, not my parents, not anyone I knew...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.08,0:18:10.61,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,The same goes for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.55,0:18:14.68,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Banri...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.12,0:18:17.89,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Banri!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.43,0:18:19.52,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Banri, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.73,0:18:23.83,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the worst...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.83,0:18:25.23,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Banri! Banri!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.77,0:18:26.73,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know that name!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.73,0:18:27.56,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Who is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.60,0:18:33.23,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You were like a bomb.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.74,0:18:38.61,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,One wrong move, and I might have lost you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.35,0:18:43.65,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't know what to do...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.18,0:18:46.65,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I forgot everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.09,0:18:49.61,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'm afraid!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.49,0:18:53.46,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so afraid, I can't help myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.63,0:18:58.66,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what I'd do if it was my fault...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.03,0:19:01.16,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Your fault?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.30,0:19:06.04,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,The day after graduation,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.04,0:19:08.81,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I went to tell you my answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.81,0:19:11.68,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,But I didn't make it in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.15,0:19:14.78,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Is it my fault?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.62,0:19:19.45,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Is it my fault because I wasn't there in time?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.55,0:19:22.11,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It can't end like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.22,0:19:25.25,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.86,0:19:31.30,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Linda-senpa-
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.01,0:19:43.98,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Tada-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.41,0:19:49.44,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Hey... What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.82,0:19:52.12,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Did something happen with Linda-senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.05,0:19:54.54,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,The answer...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.59,0:19:57.35,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,The answer is "yes"!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.59,0:20:00.19,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Tada-kun, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.19,0:20:00.96,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.60,0:20:02.90,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you running?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.90,0:20:04.02,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Please! Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.73,0:20:05.72,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Tada-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.77,0:20:09.70,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Let me borrow that!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.41,0:20:15.31,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know where this path leads.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.71,0:20:19.87,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know which paths I've chosen until now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.11,0:20:24.21,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Right and left, yes and no.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.02,0:20:29.58,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,We must continuously choose which path to take.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.76,0:20:34.42,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Yes and no are tangled in an endless web,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.96,0:20:37.40,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,and I don't know which is the right path.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.37,0:20:40.49,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,If I did...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.30,0:20:47.50,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,If I could correctly trace back all of\NTada Banri's decisions until now...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.04,0:20:52.38,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'd find Linda-senpai there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.05,0:20:54.95,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.08,0:20:58.02,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I can't turn back.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.99,0:21:01.35,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I can't find the past I've lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.79,0:21:07.62,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,If I fall again...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.60,0:21:10.56,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,...can I do everything over?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.74,0:21:16.07,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What's the answer?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.67,0:21:17.57,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Tada-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.08,0:21:27.55,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I caught you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.35,0:21:30.65,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,K-Kaga-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.85,0:21:33.48,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Don't run anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.92,0:21:38.32,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Don't go where I can't reach you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.29,0:21:41.49,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Stay with me forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.60,0:21:43.22,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.60,0:21:51.66,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I love you, Tada-kun.
